lines: at 3m, we discover and innovate in nearly every industry to help solve problems around the world.
3m premium protective overlay film with premask 1160
the brands listed above are trademarks of 3m
3m premium protective overlay film series 1160 is designed as a high performance protective transparent overlay for use on signs made from 3m sheetings, films, and images.
designed for use in areas of high dirt collection or graffiti vandalism to help restore the appearance and performance of the overlaid sign
works to keep the streets clean and safe with signs that resist permanent defacement
the film is guaranteed for the same number of years as the 3m reflective sheeting to which it is applied

developed especially for use on 3m diamond grade reflective sheeting, the 3m premium protective overlay film series 1160 is a barrier to staining by many types of graffiti, including spray paint, permanent markers, lipstick, etc.
may be cleaned using selected solvent wiping (see product bulletin 1160)
